  "materials_text": "{\"blocks\":[{\"key\":\"3cd8t\",\"text\":\"Deferiprone (DFP) (379409, Sigma Aldrich)\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"3sie8\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"8ona9\",\"text\":\"  \",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[{\"key\":0,\"offset\":0,\"length\":1}],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"9lhdo\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}}],\"entityMap\":{\"0\":{\"type\":\"reagents\",\"mutability\":\"MUTABLE\",\"data\":{\"id\":963154,\"guid\":\"457D12D5219A11EF83720A58A9FEAC02\",\"name\":\"3-Hydroxy-1,2-dimethyl-4(1H)-pyridone\",\"mol_weight\":0,\"sku\":\"379409\",\"url\":\"https://www.sigmaaldrich.com/IN/en/product/aldrich/379409\",\"cas_number\":\"30652-11-0\",\"rrid\":\"\",\"vendor\":{\"id\":17,\"name\":\"Merck MilliporeSigma (Sigma-Aldrich)\",\"link\":\"http://sigmaaldrich.com\",\"is_requested\":false,\"image\":{\"source\":\"/img/vendors/placeholder.png\",\"placeholder\":\"/img/vendors/placeholder.png\"}},\"is_public\":true,\"can_edit\":false}}}}",
  "steps": [
    "To induce mitophagy, Treat the cells for 24:00:00 with 1 millimolar (mM) Deferiprone (DFP) (379409, Sigma Aldrich), an iron chelator that mimics hypoxic conditions through stabilization of the transcription factor HIF1α and subsequent upregulation of NIX and BNIP3.",
    "Freshly dissolve the compound in sterile dH 2 O on the day itself and boil for 00:01:00 at 95 °C to dissolve the compound."
